Titulo: Stress and camber analysis of anode-supported electrolytes by tape-casting and co-firing techniques

Sentencas: However, it is very difficult to produce large area unit cells with a high degree of flatness using tape-casting and co-firing.
Titulo: Stress and camber analysis of anode-supported electrolytes by tape-casting and co-firing techniques

Sentencas: Therefore, the understanding of unit cell behavior during co-firing is very important in the manufacturing field of SOFCs.

Sentencas: The densification-based finite element method (DFEM) was selected for modeling and analysis of the co-firing behavior of a SOFC unit cell.
